WEBVTT

00:00:00.829 --> 00:00:03.048
Ninafundisha somo la kemia

00:00:03.048 --> 00:00:04.414
(Mlipuko)

00:00:04.414 --> 00:00:07.572
Sawa,Sawa.

00:00:07.572 --> 00:00:09.853
Ni zaidi ya milipuko,

00:00:09.853 --> 00:00:11.464
Kemia ipo kila mahali.

00:00:11.464 --> 00:00:14.104
Umeshawahi kuwa katika mgahawa

00:00:14.104 --> 00:00:16.449
ukiwa unajaribu kufanya hivi?

00:00:16.449 --> 00:00:18.654
Baadhi ya watu wanaitikia ndio.

00:00:18.654 --> 00:00:20.982
Hivi karibuni, niliwaonyesha wanafunzi wangu,

00:00:20.982 --> 00:00:25.331
niliwaambia waelezee kwa nini imetokea.

00:00:25.331 --> 00:00:27.952
Maswali na mazungumzo yaliyofuata

00:00:27.952 --> 00:00:29.603
yalikuwa ya kusisimua.

00:00:29.603 --> 00:00:31.417
angalia video hii ambayo Maddie